name: Jalil Evans
about: I love to help ideas grow from passing thoughts to real world products with actual impact. I'm a co-founder of a startup with the mission of improving the lives of POC on college campuses. I love to read books about business, design and self-development. I'm also an avid dancer - currently a member of Assorted Aces and BreakFree HipHop (come to our showcase!)
